title: Lil Debbie Live in Studio
itunes:title: Lil Debbie Live in Studio
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – break down the latest NFL news, including Tyrann Mathieu signing an extension with the Cardinals and wide receiver James Jones signing with the Chargers. Then, the one and only Lil Debbie stops by the studio to give her take on NFL news, Pokemon Go and more. Plus, can Marc decode Lil Debbie’s tweets?
